Ang 4 uri ng gravity ng viral pneumonia ay maaaring makita:
mild pneumonia: pulmonary edema, pneumocyte hyperplasia, malaking atypical pneumocytes, interstitial inflammation na may lymphocytic infiltration at multinucleated giant cell formation
gravy pneumonia: diffuse alveolar damage (DAD) na may diffuse alveolar exudates.
